4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience in cybersecurity. Over a 16-week program, students attend three live online classes weekly, with a maximum class size of 16. The curriculum covers essential skills such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management using data loss prevention strategies. The program also emphasizes compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop